Package: azmetr
Title: Access the AZMet API
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Eric", "Scott", , "ericrscott@arizona.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7430-7879"))
Description: Provides R functions to access the Arizona Meterological Network (AZMet) API.  Functions are more than just "thin wrappers" and do some parsing of input parameters and wrangling of output data.
